[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 5.5,
    "text": "Ever since I was a young boy growing up in Brooklyn, I have loved Spider-Man."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 5.5,
    "endTime": 6.5,
    "text": "I read the comics."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.5,
    "endTime": 8.0,
    "text": "I had the lunchbox."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.0,
    "endTime": 12.0,
    "text": "I slept on a Spider-Man pillow until I was married, I think."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.0,
    "endTime": 13.0,
    "text": "[laughter]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.0,
    "endTime": 16.0,
    "text": "And now a dream I had on that pillow is about to come true."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.2,
    "endTime": 20.0,
    "text": "Because on July 2, I will be part of the new Spider-Man movie."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.0,
    "endTime": 21.0,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.0,
    "endTime": 21.8,
    "text": "[applause]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.8,
    "endTime": 28.200000000000003,
    "text": "Now, usually Marvel is very secretive about the footage, releasing scenes from these movies."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.2,
    "endTime": 38.0,
    "text": "But in this case, for some reason, they were OK with me showing this exclusive extended excelsior scene from Spider-Man: Far From Home."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.0,
    "endTime": 42.5,
    "text": "[music playing]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.5,
    "endTime": 43.0,
    "text": "[ding]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.0,
    "endTime": 44.0,
    "text": "Hey, Joe."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.0,
    "endTime": 46.0,
    "text": "Picking up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.0,
    "endTime": 48.0,
    "text": "Hey, Peter Parker, my number one customer."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.0,
    "endTime": 49.5,
    "text": "[applause]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.5,
    "endTime": 51.0,
    "text": "Fourth time this week."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.0,
    "endTime": 51.7,
    "text": "Yeah, well, you know me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.7,
    "endTime": 53.0,
    "text": "I just love dry cleaning."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.0,
    "endTime": 54.5,
    "text": "That's what I love about you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.5,
    "endTime": 57.0,
    "text": "A lot of these Millennials, they don't care about dry cleaning."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.0,
    "endTime": 58.5,
    "text": "They've got washing machines."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.5,
    "endTime": 61.0,
    "text": "- It's disgusting, quite frankly. It really is. - It's sad, it's really sad."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.0,
    "endTime": 64.5,
    "text": "Anyway, let me get your stuff here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.5,
    "endTime": 66.0,
    "text": "Oh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.0,
    "endTime": 67.3,
    "text": "That's you, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.3,
    "endTime": 68.5,
    "text": "[laughter]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.5,
    "endTime": 69.5,
    "text": "- That's me, yes. - All right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.5,
    "endTime": 71.0,
    "text": "Thank you so much. Oh my god."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.0,
    "endTime": 72.0,
    "text": "Hey, kid, listen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.0,
    "endTime": 76.5,
    "text": "It's, uh, not my business to get into your personal balls or whatever."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.5,
    "endTime": 79.0,
    "text": "But can I ask you a question?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.0,
    "endTime": 80.5,
    "text": "Mmm, yeah, sure."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.5,
    "endTime": 82.0,
    "text": "Why you get your pajamas cleaned every two days?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.0,
    "endTime": 85.0,
    "text": "[laughter]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.0,
    "endTime": 89.5,
    "text": "Because I, uh--I sweat a lot when I sleep."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.5,
    "endTime": 90.0,
    "text": "I have a sweaty syndrome."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.0,
    "endTime": 92.5,
    "text": "- Sweaty sleep syndrome. - You're a sweaty Betty."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.5,
    "endTime": 93.3,
    "text": "[laughter] That's right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.3,
    "endTime": 94.0,
    "text": "That's correct."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.0,
    "endTime": 95.5,
    "text": "My brother was like that, you know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.5,
    "endTime": 96.5,
    "text": "- He was? Shame. - Oh, yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.5,
    "endTime": 97.7,
    "text": "He used to-- it was like a puddle."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.7,
    "endTime": 99.0,
    "text": "[laughter] We slept on bunk beds."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.0,
    "endTime": 101.0,
    "text": "He'd be on top dripping on me all night."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.0,
    "endTime": 102.3,
    "text": "- Oh, man. - It's disgusting."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.3,
    "endTime": 103.0,
    "text": "It's not good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.0,
    "endTime": 104.0,
    "text": "What about the holes?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.0,
    "endTime": 105.0,
    "text": "The hole-- the holes?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.0,
    "endTime": 106.0,
    "text": "Yeah, the holes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.0,
    "endTime": 113.5,
    "text": "It almost looked like if, uh, some kind of a mechanical octopus arm had taken a chunk out of the fabric."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.5,
    "endTime": 114.0,
    "text": "[laughter]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.0,
    "endTime": 115.3,
    "text": "That's easy to explain."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.3,
    "endTime": 119.0,
    "text": "Um, it's the, uh, um--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.0,
    "endTime": 121.0,
    "text": "- Moths? - Moths."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.0,
    "endTime": 123.0,
    "text": "- Massive moths, right. - That's what I thought it was."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.0,
    "endTime": 124.7,
    "text": "Anyway, I don't see my mask in here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.7,
    "endTime": 126.0,
    "text": "Do you have my mask?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.0,
    "endTime": 127.0,
    "text": "Oh, Connie, where's his mask?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.0,
    "endTime": 130.0,
    "text": "Under the counter, stupid."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.0,
    "endTime": 130.5,
    "text": "[laughter]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.5,
    "endTime": 132.0,
    "text": "Underneath-- oh, all right. All right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.0,
    "endTime": 134.0,
    "text": "- Hey, Connie. - Oh, here we go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.0,
    "endTime": 134.7,
    "text": "That's you, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.7,
    "endTime": 136.0,
    "text": "No, that's Matt's mask."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.0,
    "endTime": 137.5,
    "text": "Mine's the one with the white eyes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.5,
    "endTime": 139.0,
    "text": "Oh, right, right, right, right, right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.0,
    "endTime": 141.0,
    "text": "All right, here you go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.0,
    "endTime": 143.0,
    "text": "That's Wade's mask."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.0,
    "endTime": 143.5,
    "text": "White eyes with--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.5,
    "endTime": 145.0,
    "text": "Connie, it's Wade's mask."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.0,
    "endTime": 146.5,
    "text": "OK, I don't care."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.5,
    "endTime": 148.5,
    "text": "Red one. Little red."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.5,
    "endTime": 149.2,
    "text": "White eyes. That's you, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.2,
    "endTime": 150.0,
    "text": "Yeah, that's the one. Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.0,
    "endTime": 151.0,
    "text": "- Thank you. - Beautiful."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.0,
    "endTime": 152.0,
    "text": "All right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.0,
    "endTime": 153.0,
    "text": "Breaking news."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.0,
    "endTime": 161.5,
    "text": "New York's very own Spider-Man swung into action this afternoon on the Brooklyn Bridge, saving a bus full of senior citizens from certain death."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.5,
    "endTime": 169.5,
    "text": "Thanks to the masked hero's efforts, all 35 people on the bus returned home safely."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.5,
    "endTime": 173.5,
    "text": "[ominous music playing]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.5,
    "endTime": 181.0,
    "text": "That nutball on TV, he's got the same goofy PJs you got."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.0,
    "endTime": 183.0,
    "text": "He does."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.0,
    "endTime": 186.0,
    "text": "Hey, I know what's going on here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.0,
    "endTime": 188.0,
    "text": "You are an influencer."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.0,
    "endTime": 191.0,
    "text": "[laughter]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.0,
    "endTime": 193.5,
    "text": "What are you on, Instagram or Snapface?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.5,
    "endTime": 194.5,
    "text": "Snapface."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.5,
    "endTime": 195.5,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.5,
    "endTime": 198.0,
    "text": "Connie, he's on Snapface."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.0,
    "endTime": 200.0,
    "text": "Oh, I like Snapface."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.0,
    "endTime": 201.0,
    "text": "[laughter]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.0,
    "endTime": 202.5,
    "text": "Hey, give the place a little plug maybe?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.5,
    "endTime": 203.5,
    "text": "- For sure. - That'd be great."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.5,
    "endTime": 204.5,
    "text": "Absolutely."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.5,
    "endTime": 209.5,
    "text": "You truly are the best, and most gullible, dry cleaner in all of New York."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.5,
    "endTime": 211.0,
    "text": "That's what they say."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.0,
    "endTime": 212.0,
    "text": "- That's what they say. - All right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 212.0,
    "endTime": 214.0,
    "text": "- I'll see you tomorrow, kid. - I'll see you tomorrow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.0,
    "endTime": 219.0,
    "text": "Oh, hey, tell your buddy Banner to get some bigger pants."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 219.0,
    "endTime": 220.0,
    "text": "He's busting through them like crazy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 220.0,
    "endTime": 220.5,
    "text": "[laughter]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 221.0,
    "endTime": 223.0,
    "text": "He's pretty angry, but I'll try and tell him."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 223.0,
    "endTime": 224.3,
    "text": "I'm not a miracle worker."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.3,
    "endTime": 225.20000000000002,
    "text": "Yes, you are, Joe."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 225.2,
    "endTime": 226.0,
    "text": "See you later."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 226.0,
    "endTime": 227.0,
    "text": "Thanks, kid."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 227.0,
    "endTime": 230.0,
    "text": "Hey, Connie, let's go in the back and make love."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 230.0,
    "endTime": 232.0,
    "text": "OK, Joe."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 231.0,
    "endTime": 232.0,
    "text": "[laughter]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 232.0,
    "endTime": 233.0,
    "text": "[music playing]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 233.0,
    "endTime": 239.0,
    "text": "[applause]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 239.0,
    "endTime": 240.5,
    "text": "Thanks, everybody."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 240.5,
    "endTime": 242.0,
    "text": "I'm pretty happy with myself too."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 242.0,
    "endTime": 243.0,
    "text": "Thanks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 243.0,
    "endTime": 247.0,
    "text": "If you liked that video, click the subscribe button, but only if you're ready for commitment."
  }
]